- Hello.
- Hello.

372
00:27:09,210 --> 00:27:10,837
Hei, makan sebelum anda masuk!

373
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:14,591
Tiada perubahan dalam jualan tiket awal
walaupun memberikan tiket percuma?

374
00:27:15,258 --> 00:27:16,134
Tiada langsung.

375
00:27:18,678 --> 00:27:20,263
Lupakan pemasaran, kemudian.

376
00:27:21,181 --> 00:27:22,724
Berhenti membazir wang

377
00:27:22,807 --> 00:27:23,975
